gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 108, Warriors 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeat the Warriors, 108-104, and improve to 1-0 on the season. Devin Booker led the Suns with 32 points, eight assists, and six rebounds as Kevin Durant (18 points, 11 rebounds) and Jusuf Nurkic (14 points, 14 rebounds) totaled 32 points. Stephen Curry led the Warriors with 27 points and five rebounds while Klay Thompson (15 points, seven rebounds) and Chris Paul (14 points, nine assists, six rebounds) combined for 29 points. The Warriors fall to 0-1 with the loss.
